  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA32">
<l>makiḻntatu cintai tirumālē maṟṟu</l>
<l>makiḻntatuṉ pātamē pōṟṟi – makiḻnta</l>
<l>taḻalāḻi caṅka mavaipāṭi yāṭun</l>
<l>toḻilākañ cūḻntu tuṇintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Exulted is [my] mind, o Tirumāl, moreover,</l>
<l>exulted, praising your feet, exulted,</l>
<l>singing of these: the fiery diskus [and] the conch,</l>
<l>– with concentration, encompassing [your] body in the act of dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
